org.sql: SELECT DISTINCT spree_variants.* FROM spree_variants INNER JOIN spree_prices ON spree_prices.deleted_at IS NULL AND spree_prices.variant_id = spree_variants.id WHERE spree_variants.deleted_at IS NULL AND spree_prices.currency = 'EUR' AND spree_prices.amount IS NOT NULL
